CONTRIBUTING TO THE CHANGES IN EARNED PREMIUMS IN EACH SEGMENT IN 2012 AND 2011 COMPARED WITH THE RESPECTIVE PRIOR YEAR ARE DISCUSSED IN MORE DETAIL IN THE SEGMENT DISCUSSIONS

