REALIZED INVESTMENT GAINS RELATED TO EQUITY SECURITIES AND $41 MILLION OF NET REALIZED INVESTMENT GAINS RELATED TO OTHER INVESTMENTS, PARTIALLY OFFSET BY NET REALIZED INVESTMENT LOSSES OF $62 MILLION

ASSOCIATED WITH U.S. TREASURY FUTURES CONTRACTS.

