IN

JANUARY 2012, STANDARD & POOR'S DOWNGRADED THE SOVEREIGN RATINGS OF NINE EUROZONE COUNTRIES, INCLUDING FRANCE (FROM "AAA" TO "AA+"). IN NOVEMBER 2012, MOODY'S

