DISCOUNT AND THE DEDUCTION OF UNDERWRITING EXPENSES AND COMMISSIONS AND OTHER EXPENSES, WERE APPROXIMATELY $496 MILLION AND $738 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY. INTEREST ON THE SENIOR NOTES IS

