PLANS, EXPECTED MARGIN IMPROVEMENT, FUTURE PENSION PLAN CONTRIBUTIONS AND THE POTENTIAL IMPACT OF INVESTMENT MARKETS AND OTHER ECONOMIC CONDITIONS ON THE COMPANY'S INVESTMENT

