BRAZIL. JMALUCELLI IS CURRENTLY THE MARKET LEADER IN SURETY IN BRAZIL BASED ON MARKET SHARE, AND COMMENCED WRITING OTHER PROPERTY AND CASUALTY INSURANCE BUSINESS IN 2012. THE COMPANY'S INVESTMENT IN

