HOMEOWNERS

POLICIES PROVIDE PROTECTION AGAINST LOSSES TO DWELLINGS AND CONTENTS FROM A VARIETY OF PERILS (EXCLUDING FLOODING) AS WELL AS COVERAGE FOR PERSONAL LIABILITY. THE COMPANY

WRITES HOMEOWNERS INSURANCE FOR DWELLINGS, CONDOMINIUMS AND TENANTS, AND RENTAL PROPERTIES. THE COMPANY WRITES COVERAGE FOR BOATS AND YACHTS AND VALUABLE PERSONAL ITEMS SUCH AS JEWELRY, AND ALSO

