MORTGAGE-BACKED SECURITIES, WHICH INCLUDE PASS-THROUGH SECURITIES AND COLLATERALIZED MORTGAGE OBLIGATIONS (CMO). INCLUDED IN THE TOTALS AT DECEMBER 31, 2012 AND 2011 WERE

