AVERAGE CREDIT RATING OF THE $893 MILLION AND $1.05 BILLION OF NON-GUARANTEED CMO HOLDINGS AT DECEMBER 31, 2012 AND 2011, RESPECTIVELY, WAS "B2" AND "BA1,"

RESPECTIVELY. THE AVERAGE CREDIT RATING OF ALL OF THE ABOVE SECURITIES WAS "A1" AND "AA3" AT DECEMBER 31, 2012 AND 2011, RESPECTIVELY.

