DATA WHICH RESULTED IN A TRANSFER OUT OF LEVEL 3 INTO LEVEL 2. IN PRIOR PERIODS, THESE SECURITIES WERE VALUED INTERNALLY USING UNOBSERVABLE INPUTS.

THE

COMPANY HAD NO MATERIAL ASSETS OR LIABILITIES THAT WERE MEASURED AT FAIR VALUE ON A NON-RECURRING BASIS DURING THE YEARS ENDED DECEMBER 31, 2012 AND 2011.

